isAustralian-tour-dates-announcement-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/OasisAustralian-tour-dates-announcement-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/OasisAustralian-tour-dates-announcement-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/OasisAustralian-tour-dates-announcement-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3800092" class="wp-caption-text"> Oasis的Liam和Noel Gallagher。学分：西蒙·埃米特（Simon Emmett）</figcaption></figure><p>关于乐队构成的谣言工厂已经看到许多过去的成员名字进入了竞争。最初，有报道<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-rumoured-to-reform-with-only-the-gallagher-brothers-and-no-other-original-members-3787367">称：“预计没有其他原始绿洲成员会加入聚会”</a> ，而诺埃尔·加拉格尔（Noel Gallagher）<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noel-gallaghers-high-flying-birds">高空飞行鸟</a>的成员将介入该小组的其他成员。</p><p>鼓手<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/alan-white-teases-joining-oasis-reunion-line-up-3789548">艾伦·怀特（Alan White）去年在他用旋转的联盟杰克设计（Jack Design）张贴了鼓工套件的图像之后，引起了粉丝的交谈</a>，而原始的棍棒<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/former-oasis-drummer-tony-mccarroll-opens-up-about-reunion-tour-3789516">托尼·麦卡罗尔（Tony McCarroll）说，乐队“尚未伸出援手</a>，老实说，我没有屏住呼吸”。</p><p>常客保罗·“ Bonehead” Arthurs，Gem Archer，Andy Bell，Zak Starkey，Jessica Greenfield，Russell Pritchard，Chris Sharrock，Mike Rowe <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/oasis-reunion-line-up-band-members-guide-3788552">也在桌上</a>。上周，利亚姆开玩笑地嘲笑了一个由Peppa Pig，<em>芝麻街</em>的Bert和Ernie和Finger Bobs组成的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-clears-everything-up-with-joke-about-rumoured-oasis-band-line-up-here-we-have-it-3843750">阵容</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3791232" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3791232" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3791232" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/oasis-perform-live.jpg" alt="绿洲" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/oasis-perform-live.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/oasis-perform-live-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/oasis-perform-live-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/oasis-perform-live-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/oasis-perform-live-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/oasis-perform-live-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3791232" class="wp-caption-text">绿洲在1997年表演。信贷：Simon Ritter/Redferns</figcaption></figure><p>现在，与乐队和Tour紧密合作的消息人士告诉<em>NME</em> ，以下成员将组成今年夏天的绿洲日期的现场乐队：</p><h2><strong>安迪·贝尔 - 低音</strong></h2><p>长期以来，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/andy-bell">安迪·贝尔（Andy Bell）</a>长期以来恢复了折叠，据说安迪·贝尔（Andy Bell）从1999年至2009年登上了Paul“ Guigsy” McGuigan的贝斯，然后才跟随利亚姆（Liam）进入衍生乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/BEADY-EYE">Beady Beady Eye</a> 。除了成为Indie Heroes <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ride">Ride</a>的成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mantra-of-the-cosmos">，</a>最近与《<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/happy-mondays">周六快乐的</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shaun-ryder">Shaun Ryder》</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bez">Bez</a> （他们还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallagher-joins-mantra-of-the-cosmos-psychedelic-new-single-domino-bones-gets-dangerous-3827005">丢弃了Noel Gallagher的单人</a>），最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/andy-bell-announces-solo-album-pinball-wanderer-featuring-former-oasis-bandmate-gem-archer-3827436">发行了他的第三张个人专辑“ Pinball Wanderer</a> ”  - 这也以他的旧Oasis Bandmate和Longmate Commaporator Gem Archer regertareard。 </p><figure id="attachment_3845388" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3845388" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3845388" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ANDY_BELL_OASIS_REUNION_COMP.jpg" alt="安迪·贝尔（Andy Bell）于2005年与利亚姆·加拉格尔（Liam Gallagher）一起在绿洲，并在2024年登上舞台。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ANDY_BELL_OASIS_REUNION_COMP.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ANDY_BELL_OASIS_REUNION_COMP-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ANDY_BELL_OASIS_REUNION_COMP-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ANDY_BELL_OASIS_REUNION_COMP-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ANDY_BELL_OASIS_REUNION_COMP-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ANDY_BELL_OASIS_REUNION_COMP-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3845388" class="wp-caption-text">安迪·贝尔（Andy Bell）于2005年与利亚姆·加拉格尔（Liam Gallagher）一起在绿洲，并在2024年登上舞台。</figcaption></figure><h2><strong>宝石弓箭手 - 吉他</strong></h2><p>说到谁，我们被告知阿切尔将回到吉他。伯纳黑德（Bonehead）出发后介入，阿切尔（Archer）也将从1999年至2009年与Oasis一起玩 - 然后继续与Gallaghers一起工作，这是Beady Eye和Noel的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/NOEL-GALLAGHERS-HIGH-FLYING-BIRDS">高空飞鸟</a>的一部分。这些岁月还将他视为Heavy Stereo的一部分，骄傲的玛丽和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paul-weller">保罗·韦勒（Paul Weller）</a>之类的合作者。 </p><figure id="attachment_3845390" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3845390" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3845390" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/gem_archer_oasis_line_up.jpg" alt="诺埃尔·加拉格尔（Noel Gallagher）和宝石阿切尔（Gem Archer）于2024年7月21日在英格兰沃里克（Warwick）在沃里克城堡（Warwick Castle）与高空飞鸟一起表演。 （史蒂夫·索恩（Steve Thorne/Redferns）的照片）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/gem_archer_oasis_line_up.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/gem_archer_oasis_line_up-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/gem_archer_oasis_line_up-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/gem_archer_oasis_line_up-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/gem_archer_oasis_line_up-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/gem_archer_oasis_line_up-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3845390" class="wp-caption-text">诺埃尔·加拉格尔（Noel Gallagher）和宝石阿切尔（Gem Archer）于2024年7月21日在英格兰沃里克（Warwick）在沃里克城堡（Warwick Castle）与高空飞鸟一起表演。 （史蒂夫·索恩（Steve Thorne/Redferns）的照片）</figcaption></figure><h2><strong>保罗“骨头”亚瑟 - 吉他</strong></h2><p>自从OFF以来，心爱的Bonehead一直与Oasis团聚阵容有关，他在成功的岁月中与Liam成为独奏艺术家的舞台定期固定。现在，我们了解到，亚瑟（Arthurs）今年夏天将与诺埃尔（Noel）和弓箭手（Noel）和弓箭手（Noel）和阿切尔（Archer）一起乘坐吉他。 </p><figure id="attachment_3845391" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3845391" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3845391" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bonehead_oasis_line_up.jpg" alt="Bonehead和Liam Gallagher将于2019年11月28日在英国伦敦的O2竞技场演出。 （洛恩·汤姆森（Lorne Thomson）/雷德弗恩（Lorne Thomson）的照片）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bonehead_oasis_line_up.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bonehead_oasis_line_up-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bonehead_oasis_line_up-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bonehead_oasis_line_up-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bonehead_oasis_line_up-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bonehead_oasis_line_up-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3845391" class="wp-caption-text"> Bonehead和Liam Gallagher将于2019年11月28日在英国伦敦的O2竞技场演出。 （洛恩·汤姆森（Lorne Thomson）/雷德弗恩（Lorne Thomson）的照片）</figcaption></figure><h2><strong>乔伊·沃隆克（Joey Waronker） - 鼓</strong></h2><p>One of the <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-says-there-could-be-a-few-new-faces-in-oasis-reunion-tour-band-3795146">“new faces” that Liam teased</a> would be part of the line-up, Joey Waronker is an esteemed and prolific drummer and producer who has played with the likes of <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/BECK">Beck</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/r-e-m">REM</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/elliott-smith">Elliott Smith</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/roger-waters">Roger Waters</a> , as well as being a member of <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/THOM-YORKE">Thom Yorke</a> &#39;s <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ATOMS-FOR-PEACE">Atoms For Peace</a> band and experimental rock outfit <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ultraista">Ultraísta</a> with <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/NIGEL-GODRICH">Nigel Godrich</a> .他可能以前从未玩过Oasis，但他在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/liam-gallagher-john-squire-tracklist-lyrics-3593699">Liam和John Squire的Live Band Touring去年合作专辑</a>中落后于鼓工套件。靠近乐队和巡回演出的消息人士告诉<em>NME</em> ，营地对在聚会阵容上有如此受人尊敬的Muso感到兴奋。 </p><figure id="attachment_3845394" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3845394" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3845394" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/JOEY_WARONKER_OASIS_LINE_UP.jpg" alt="乔伊·沃恩克（Joey Waronker）于2024年与贝克（Beck）一起在舞台上，并在2027年在洛杉矶演出。信贷：Miikka Skaffari/Scott Dudelson/Getty Images" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/JOEY_WARONKER_OASIS_LINE_UP.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/JOEY_WARONKER_OASIS_LINE_UP-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/JOEY_WARONKER_OASIS_LINE_UP-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/JOEY_WARONKER_OASIS_LINE_UP-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/JOEY_WARONKER_OASIS_LINE_UP-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/JOEY_WARONKER_OASIS_LINE_UP-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3845394" class="wp-caption-text">乔伊·沃恩克（Joey Waronker）于2024年与贝克（Beck）一起在舞台上，并于2017年在洛杉矶演出。信贷：Miikka Skaffari/Scott Dudelson/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p><em>绿洲的“ Live &#39;25</em>聚会之旅”将于7月4日星期五在加的夫开始，将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-tour-uk-ireland-stadium-2025-liam-noel-gallagher-tickets-3787539">英国长期的约会视为他们今年在欧洲唯一的演出</a>，然后乐队前往<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-announce-2025-reunion-tour-dates-in-north-america-and-mexico-buy-tickets-3798246">北美</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-announce-2025-south-american-reunion-tour-dates-the-brothers-are-coming-buy-tickets-3809661">南美</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-announce-australian-dates-of-live-25-reunion-tour-buy-tickets-3800091">澳大利亚</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-announce-south-korean-and-japan-dates-for-their-2025-reunion-tour-3814881">亚洲的</a>体育场。</p><p>乐队在最初公告的粉丝向粉丝的声明中分享：</p><p> <em><strong>“枪支已经沉默了。</strong></em><br /><em><strong>星星已经对齐。</strong></em><br /><em><strong>伟大的等待结束了。</strong></em><br /><em><strong>来看看。</strong></em><br /><em><strong>它不会电视转播。”</strong></em></p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/oasis-reunion-liam-noel-gallagher-3787549">您必须与之相关：通往绿洲超音速返回的岩石之路</a></strong></li></ul><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-fans-react-to-ticketmasters-dynamic-pricing-3789361">由于动态“激增”定价的做法</a>（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/uk-government-price-cap-ticket-touts-secondary-dynamic-consultation-chris-bryant-interview-3827671">现在由政府进行调查</a>），出售给英国腿的门票引起了争议，票务司机<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/thousands-of-oasis-tickets-are-now-being-cancelled-by-ticketmaster-in-bot-crackdown-but-many-fans-are-unhappy-3836142">最近取消了数千张门票，这些票被认为是由机器人购买的，</a>以竞争，以镇压二级票务网站和潮流（ <a href="https:/